    },
    {
      "id": "t_data", "type": "text", "x": 485, "y": 308, "width": 330, "height": 85,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a9a", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 10003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 10004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "onDataReady()  // RunLoop fires this\nlock(handlerMutex)\nrecvSignal() → readFrame(rxRing)\n\nRESPONSE → match seq → wake caller via cv\nNOTIFY   → onNotification() → onBarNotify()\n\n// no receiver thread!",
      "originalText": "onDataReady()  // RunLoop fires this\nlock(handlerMutex)\nrecvSignal() → readFrame(rxRing)\n\nRESPONSE → match seq → wake caller via cv\nNOTIFY   → onNotification() → onBarNotify()\n\n// no receiver thread!",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "cli_data", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "cli_call", "type": "rectangle", "x": 480, "y": 420, "width": 340, "height": 80,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#e67700", "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "aA",
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 11001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 11002,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"id": "t_call", "type": "text"}],
      "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_call", "type": "text", "x": 485, "y": 428, "width": 330, "height": 65,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "aAa", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 11003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 11004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "call() — from ANY thread (not the RunLoop thread)\nwriteFrame(txRing) → sendSignal()\ncv.wait() — blocks caller until onDataReady()\n              delivers the matching response\n\n⚠ call() from RunLoop thread = DEADLOCK",
      "originalText": "call() — from ANY thread (not the RunLoop thread)\nwriteFrame(txRing) → sendSignal()\ncv.wait() — blocks caller until onDataReady()\n              delivers the matching response\n\n⚠ call() from RunLoop thread = DEADLOCK",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "cli_call", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "comparison", "type": "rectangle", "x": 40, "y": 650, "width": 800, "height": 100,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "aB",
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 12001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 12002,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"id": "t_comp", "type": "text"}],
      "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_comp", "type": "text", "x": 45, "y": 658, "width": 790, "height": 85,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "aBa", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 12003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 12004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Thread-per-client (default, loop=nullptr)         RunLoop mode (loop=&runLoop)\n─────────────────────────────────────────          ─────────────────────────────────────────\n1 accept thread + 1 receiver thread per client     0 extra threads — all on RunLoop thread\nSimple, works everywhere                           Efficient, scales to many clients\nBlocking recvSignal() per thread                   Event-driven: addSource() per client fd\nWindows: works today                               Windows: needs overlapped I/O (Phase 5)",
      "originalText": "Thread-per-client (default, loop=nullptr)         RunLoop mode (loop=&runLoop)\n─────────────────────────────────────────          ─────────────────────────────────────────\n1 accept thread + 1 receiver thread per client     0 extra threads — all on RunLoop thread\nSimple, works everywhere                           Efficient, scales to many clients\nBlocking recvSignal() per thread                   Event-driven: addSource() per client fd\nWindows: works today                               Windows: needs overlapped I/O (Phase 5)",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "comparison", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

